### Send a raw string message to my-topic (StringSerializer)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages/send
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello Kafka

### Send a JSON Package to my-topic
### NOTE: requires switching my-topic's producer/consumer serializers in application.yml
### from String(De)Serializer to Json(De)Serializer first - see CLAUDE.md.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages/send-json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "sample-package"
}

### Kick off the Wikimedia recent-changes stream -> wikimedia-updates topic
### Fire-and-forget: response returns immediately, watch the app log (WikiMediaConsumer)
### for incoming messages.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages/see-update
